column5: Excellent pics guys...  Mine is a pic of Glace Bay harbour where I spent many a day fishing for smelts in my younger years, and the far shoreline where we spent lots of time swimming and hanging out..
This pic was taken in West Bay Lake Nipissing as the sun was setting below the horizon....
